  <font color="White">driving in the real world?"</font>

01:11.200 --> 01:13.000
  It's pretty simple, really.

01:13.000 --> 01:14.640
<font color="White">When you get through the training,</font>

01:14.640 --> 01:17.320
   <font color="White">you should find it easier      
  to concentrate on everything</font>

01:17.320 --> 01:20.560
   <font color="White">that's going on around you     
        and on the road.</font>

01:20.560 --> 01:23.479
  You'll also find it easier      
  <font color="White">to shift your concentration</font>

01:23.479 --> 01:25.760
   <font color="White">from one thing to another.</font>

01:25.760 --> 01:28.879
 It's important that you follow   
   <font color="White">the instructions carefully</font>

01:28.879 --> 01:30.080
      <font color="White">and whatever you do,</font>

01:30.080 --> 01:33.560
     <font color="White">don't try and complete       
all the training in one session.</font>

01:33.560 --> 01:37.040
